originalText.text: I’ve been going to Mane Advocate for 21 years. Tamara is the only hair care professional that cuts my hair. I’ve had 3 big chops and my hair always comes back healthy. I would recommend this salon for anyone with scalp issues or just needs special attention paid to their crown. Tamara is always on it!

originalText.text: Great owner (review is just for Tamara) that really promotes healthy hair for all her costumers. Clean space and a chill vibe, with the news on cc and nice music playing in the background. Prices are fair and her advice for home care is free. She also provides a bag of chips when you sit under the dryer.

originalText.text: I love Tamara.  She’s been doing my hair for 10 years and I’m always pleased.  She is pleasant and smart and knows her stuff.  Continually engaged in learning whatever’s new and perfecting her craft.  I trust her immensely.
